About Us

Uplevel Systems provides secure hybrid managed networking services that address small business IT and security needs.  The Unbox services include managed firewall, router, switch, VPN, NAS, Wi-Fi, cloud backup and managed access in an integrated platform that is easy to deploy, configure and manage from a standard browser or mobile device.


Our Ideal Customer

The ideal customer for the Uplevel Systems Unbox solutions are small businesses with 1-50 employees that require a secure, powerful and flexible network that can scale with their business and is affordable.  We address the networking and security needs for companies that have outgrown the "big-box" consumer grade gear, and that can't afford to spend $1000s of dollars on a complex and customized enterprise solutions that are not optimized for their needs.





